             <div class="headline">
              <a href="page/about">
               <h2 class="large">
                Research Safety at The Gordon Center
               </h2>
               <p class="blurb whitealpha hidden-phone hidden-tablet">
                Proper safety equipment, such as eye protection worn by these scientists working with lasers, is essential for conducting world class research.
                <span class="fake-link ss-standard ss-navigateright right">
                 Learn more about our mission
                </span>
               </p>
              </a>
             </div>
             <img alt="" src="https://researchsafety.uchicago.edu/sites/researchsafety.uchicago.edu/files/styles/homefeature-large/public/uploads/images/GC-2006_0.jpg?itok=LrxehS1t" title="Photo by Jason Smith"/>
            </li>
           </ul>
