             <span>
              <img alt="" src="https://researchsafety.uchicago.edu/sites/researchsafety.uchicago.edu/files/styles/columnwidth-wider/public/uploads/images/Lab%20Safety%20from%20Website.jpeg?itok=Frp__9Kn"/>
             </span>
             <h2>
              Safety in the Laboratory
             </h2>
             <p>
              To ensure safe practices in the lab, please refer to our safety manuals and emergency/spill reponse protocols on the
              <a href="/page/policies-and-safety-manuals">
               Safety Manuals
              </a>
              page.
             </p>
